I"R<p>They love me…they love me not.</p>

<p>I feel by now I have a pretty good handle on the question. I don’t have to pick the petals of a poor flower: my body could tell.</p>

<p>This is my attempt to reflect on the instances I’ve been wrong, if I ever have been, and when I have been right, and how to tell one from the other.</p>
